NOTE ON DATA LICENSING

The source code in this repository is licensed under the MIT License above.

The benchmark datasets (under data/) are released under Creative Commons
Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0). They include data derived from:
  - World Bank Open Data (population, GDP, consumer price inflation) — via the
    datahub "datasets" mirrors; licensed ODC-PDDL-1.0 / CC-BY-4.0.
  - CDIAC fossil-fuel CO2 emissions by nation — via the datahub mirror;
    licensed ODC-PDDL-1.0.
Per-source provenance and licenses are recorded in
data/sources_real/provenance.json. Synthetic tiers are original work.
